            A passionate technology professional with expertise in software development, project management, and systems integration.
          </p>
          <div class="footer-social">
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/kudakwashe-taderera" class="social-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
